<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NMT51">
<l>eṉakkāvā rāroruva rēyem perumāṉ</l>
<l>taṉakkāvāṉ tāṉēmaṟ ṟallāṟ puṉakkāyā</l>
<l>vaṇṇaṉē yuṉṉaip piṟaraṟiyā reṉmatikku</l>
<l>viṇṇellā muṇṭō vilai</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O You of the hue of ironwood-flowers from the uplands!</l>
<l>Who ever is equal to me?  Our Lord is His own equal, but not [mine]!</l>
<l>The others do not know You.</l>
<l>Is the whole sky [of equal] value to my mind?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
